This is usually measured through established research methodologies under the term “usability testing,” which includes success rates and customer satisfaction. While UX encompasses designing the overall experience of a product, usability focuses on the mechanics of making sure products work as well as possible for the user.

og_description: Please fill out the following form to kick off the exploratory process in working with the Presidential Innovation Fellows (PIF) program. You can see example project descriptions on our website (e.g. https://presidentialinnovationfellows.gov/projects/va-cto/)We are currently accepting project submissions through April for the next cohort of fellows. Fellows are hired as full-time federal employees at a GS-15 level, Step 1, serving a 1-2 year term in Washington, D.C.
